1
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:32,320
♪During the dark night♪

2
00:00:32,900 --> 00:00:34,940
♪A guiding light♪

3
00:00:34,940 --> 00:00:36,920
♪Just like you♪

4
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:42,290
♪Makes life turn bright♪

5
00:00:42,550 --> 00:00:47,540
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

6
00:00:47,540 --> 00:00:51,130
♪You gave me strength♪

7
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:53,810
♪Running for truth♪

8
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:58,440
♪I find my path♪

9
00:00:58,680 --> 00:01:03,090
♪Drawing on the hope♪

10
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:06,740
♪That you render me♪

11
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,870
♪In this long journey♪

12
00:01:09,870 --> 00:01:13,940
♪I run on lightly♪

13
00:01:30,820 --> 00:01:33,120
=Reborn=

14
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:35,080
(Adapted from the serialized work "Reborn"
by Qiang Yu)

15
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,790
Your uncle asked me to come by

16
00:01:36,790 --> 00:01:38,150
just for peace of mind.

17
00:01:38,150 --> 00:01:40,460
Make sure she doesn't have
another episode and wander off.

18
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:43,560
Remind your uncle that

19
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,950
he needs to keep a close eye on her.

20
00:01:45,544 --> 00:01:46,984
She can't take another shock.

21
00:01:48,790 --> 00:01:49,950
Madam Xiuzhen,

22
00:01:49,950 --> 00:01:51,980
you're a health worker
at the village clinic?

23
00:01:51,980 --> 00:01:52,510
That's right.

24
00:01:52,510 --> 00:01:53,950
Over 20 years now.

25
00:01:53,950 --> 00:01:55,520
Every illness in this village,

26
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:56,540
I usually know about it.

27
00:01:57,340 --> 00:01:59,230
Then do you know about Qiao Beiyu?

28
00:02:01,870 --> 00:02:03,150
Beiyu, huh...

29
00:02:03,150 --> 00:02:04,950
Of course I heard the rumors.

30
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:06,540
Everyone was talking.

31
00:02:06,540 --> 00:02:08,670
But whether she really
had that kind of illness,

32
00:02:08,670 --> 00:02:09,820
I don't know.

33
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:12,700
One thing though,

34
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:15,140
I remember very clearly.

35
00:02:20,540 --> 00:02:23,630
During the winter holidays, when Beiyu
returned from Huanzhou Art School,

36
00:02:23,630 --> 00:02:26,230
she had a miscarriage
and came to the clinic.

37
00:02:26,951 --> 00:02:29,540
Soon after, your mother came here too.

38
00:02:30,860 --> 00:02:31,860
Fanghao.

39
00:02:34,140 --> 00:02:34,910
Mom.

40
00:02:38,230 --> 00:02:38,700
Mom.

41
00:02:53,190 --> 00:02:54,670
A little girl in her twenties

42
00:02:54,670 --> 00:02:56,110
suffered a miscarriage.

43
00:02:56,110 --> 00:02:56,740
How pitiful.

44
00:02:57,230 --> 00:02:58,110
The news

45
00:02:58,110 --> 00:02:59,790
wasn't spread
by the people at the clinic.

46
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:03,020
However, bad news spread quickly.

47
00:03:03,510 --> 00:03:05,300
Bei was too careless as well.

48
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,350
She suffered from such a misfortune
at a young age,

49
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:08,820
but she still didn't learn her lesson.

50
00:03:09,820 --> 00:03:12,390
Later, she became worse.

51
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:15,580
Do you know who's that person?

52
00:03:15,580 --> 00:03:18,070
I don't know who he is,

53
00:03:18,070 --> 00:03:19,860
but with the kind of lifestyle
she is living,

54
00:03:20,950 --> 00:03:22,950
the rumors are probably true.

55
00:03:22,950 --> 00:03:25,630
She can't blame other people
for badmouthing her.

56
00:03:26,950 --> 00:03:27,820
I'm leaving.

57
00:03:30,297 --> 00:03:39,180
=Episode 4=
(Lie? Truth!)

58
00:03:39,231 --> 00:03:41,985
(Ming Qiuxin:
Wait until I get off work if you're free.)

59
00:03:42,322 --> 00:03:43,540
(Let's eat together.)

60
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:55,820
What a coincidence.

61
00:03:57,020 --> 00:03:59,390
A major surgery was cancelled suddenly.

62
00:04:00,910 --> 00:04:02,910
I get a few hours of break.

63
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:05,630
We can have a meal together.

64
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:10,700
Dr. Ming, do you still remember
what my favourite food is?

65
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:12,390
You've liked pizza since you were young.

66
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:15,980
There's a new pizza shop
in front of the hospital.

67
00:04:15,980 --> 00:04:17,030
We can give it a try.

68
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:19,270
I liked eating pizza when I was young,

69
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:21,860
but that was when I was six or seven.

70
00:04:23,230 --> 00:04:25,300
I'm 17 years old now.

71
00:04:25,300 --> 00:04:26,710
I've stopped eating pizza

72
00:04:27,180 --> 00:04:28,670
since my mother left me.

73
00:04:29,380 --> 00:04:29,980
It was you

74
00:04:31,150 --> 00:04:32,790
who made me leave my mother since young.

75
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:35,740
You didn't even tell me

76
00:04:35,740 --> 00:04:37,030
when my grandfather was dying.

77
00:04:39,910 --> 00:04:42,420
You were preparing
for your high school exam.

78
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,400
I was afraid
that it might affect your studies.

79
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,060
Was my high school exam important?

80
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,830
Was the biology competition important?

81
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,740
Were they more important

82
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:58,620
than my bond with Grandpa and Mom?

83
00:04:58,620 --> 00:04:59,640
They were all in the past.

84
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,880
There's no need to mention it.

85
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:01,540
Let's eat.

86
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:05,830
I tried to understand you

87
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:08,060
but you've never changed.

88
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:11,180
Have dinner on your own.

89
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:24,620
(You only care about your patients)

90
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:25,620
(and your surgeries.)

91
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,540
(What about Sheng and me?)

92
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:29,030
(Have you cared about us?)

93
00:05:29,030 --> 00:05:30,180
I can see

94
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:31,380
all the sacrifices you've made.

95
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,540
Can you understand
where I'm coming from?

96
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:34,540
I did

97
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,710
and I sympathized with you.

98
00:05:36,710 --> 00:05:37,500
(What about you?)

99
00:05:38,080 --> 00:05:39,150
(Sheng also needs a father)

100
00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:41,030
(who can grow up with him.)

101
00:05:41,670 --> 00:05:42,160
(I'm sorry.)

102
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,240
(I don't need your apology.)

103
00:05:44,470 --> 00:05:46,380
You can be summoned
by a phone call every time.

104
00:05:46,380 --> 00:05:47,540
(Every time!)

105
00:05:48,470 --> 00:05:50,230
(Why must I and Sheng
sacrifice ourselves)

106
00:05:50,230 --> 00:05:52,380
(to make you into a good doctor?)

107
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:54,350
(I've had enough of this life.)

108
00:05:55,940 --> 00:05:58,270
Mom, don't go.

109
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:07,670
Mom!

110
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:25,620
(Let me carry you.)

111
00:06:26,180 --> 00:06:26,620
(Good.)

112
00:06:27,710 --> 00:06:28,270
(Slowly.)

113
00:06:32,620 --> 00:06:33,270
All right.

114
00:06:37,030 --> 00:06:37,620
(Slowly.)

115
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,030
(Are you standing still?)

116
00:06:39,670 --> 00:06:40,300
(Yes.)

117
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:41,590
(All right.)

118
00:06:43,710 --> 00:06:44,540
(Hold me.)

119
00:06:44,860 --> 00:06:45,470
(It's fine.)

120
00:06:45,470 --> 00:06:46,030
(Stand still.)

121
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:48,230
Sheng, listen.

122
00:06:48,790 --> 00:06:49,740
To what?

123
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:52,670
The leaves are rustling in the wind.

124
00:06:55,940 --> 00:06:58,380
The birds are singing.

125
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:01,150
Sheng, look.

126
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:03,710
There's a bird.

127
00:07:05,270 --> 00:07:06,270
It's flying past.

128
00:07:07,030 --> 00:07:09,230
The sound of waves made by the river.

129
00:07:09,230 --> 00:07:10,110
Do you hear it?

130
00:07:10,910 --> 00:07:12,350
When you are in a bad mood,

131
00:07:12,350 --> 00:07:14,230
listen to the sounds of nature.

132
00:07:14,230 --> 00:07:15,620
They are magical.

133
00:07:16,590 --> 00:07:17,470
The more you listen,

134
00:07:17,470 --> 00:07:20,110
the calmer you'll feel.

135
00:07:20,110 --> 00:07:22,420
Then, you'll be able
to forget all the noise.

136
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:23,150
All right?

137
00:07:23,150 --> 00:07:23,830
All right.

138
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:25,180
Give it a try.

139
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:46,030
Hello, is it Ming Sheng?

140
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:47,590
Hello.

141
00:07:48,740 --> 00:07:50,350
I want to talk to my mother.

142
00:07:51,150 --> 00:07:52,030
Sorry.

143
00:07:52,030 --> 00:07:53,600
Anna is in the recording booth now.

144
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,590
If it's something urgent,

145
00:07:54,590 --> 00:07:55,830
I'll tell her after she's done.

146
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:57,300
It's nothing.

147
00:07:57,740 --> 00:07:58,590
Forget it, then.

148
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:18,710
(Have you seen it?)

149
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:24,120
(Huanzhou People's Hospital,
Qiao Beiyu's Scanned Medical Records)

150
00:08:26,657 --> 00:08:28,810
(Report of HIV Antibody
Confirmatory Testing)

151
00:08:28,820 --> 00:08:30,500
(Qiao Beiyu)

152
00:08:32,457 --> 00:08:35,950
(Conclusion, Positive)

153
00:08:36,590 --> 00:08:37,710
(I've contacted them.)

154
00:08:37,710 --> 00:08:39,620
(The hospital will mail it later.)

155
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:41,350
(Remember to receive it.)

156
00:08:43,740 --> 00:08:45,020
(Sometimes,)

157
00:08:45,020 --> 00:08:47,310
(we try our best to find the answer,)

158
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:50,430
(and when we finally do,)

159
00:08:50,430 --> 00:08:52,470
(even though everything is resolved,)

160
00:08:52,470 --> 00:08:54,190
(it also means)

161
00:08:54,190 --> 00:08:56,140
(all our efforts were in vain.)

162
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,260
There's a lot of rain this year.

163
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:02,160
There's waterlogging of fruit trees.

164
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:02,980
Most trees are dead.

165
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,720
If we don't spray some insecticide
to get rid of pests,

166
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,240
we won't have any crops to harvest.

167
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:07,900
Qingyu!

168
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:09,900
Doesn't the land
belong to Uncle Haisheng's family?

169
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:11,860
Why do they order us
to work for them for free?

170
00:09:13,830 --> 00:09:15,350
Why isn't she back yet?

171
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:17,860
We are all a family.

172
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:19,430
What are you talking about?

173
00:09:19,430 --> 00:09:20,350
Besides,

174
00:09:20,830 --> 00:09:23,110
didn't you eat Uncle Haisheng's fruit?

175
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:24,310
How can you put your feet here?

176
00:09:24,310 --> 00:09:26,190
Haisheng was a clerk in the village,

177
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:27,660
but he lost his job.

178
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:31,000
I can't even move my feet.

179
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,830
I'm staying home for two days
starting tomorrow.

180
00:09:34,110 --> 00:09:36,120
Put your legs down. That's very rude.

181
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,240
Jiangsheng, have some water.

182
00:09:37,830 --> 00:09:38,950
I'm not drinking.

183
00:09:38,950 --> 00:09:40,500
Give me a glass.

184
00:09:40,500 --> 00:09:41,310
Me too.

185
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:53,360
You're back?

186
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,560
Do you know what time it is?

187
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,500
Why are you so late?

188
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:57,950
I went to the library.

189
00:09:59,070 --> 00:09:59,900
Don't you know

190
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:00,980
what time it is?

191
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:03,900
I forgot about the time.

192
00:10:03,900 --> 00:10:05,560
It's a good thing
for Qing to love to study.

193
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:07,120
Those who study at Huanzhou High School

194
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,710
can all get
into a famous high university.

195
00:10:09,070 --> 00:10:10,470
Just enjoy the rest of your life.

196
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:11,900
I'm going back to my room.

197
00:10:12,430 --> 00:10:13,710
Me too.

198
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:16,020
Qingyu.

199
00:10:18,470 --> 00:10:19,430
I'm being serious.

200
00:10:20,830 --> 00:10:22,020
It's very late

201
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:23,260
and it's dark.

202
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:25,230
What if you encounter a bad person?

203
00:10:25,780 --> 00:10:26,470
Every girl

204
00:10:26,470 --> 00:10:28,020
is already home at this hour.

205
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:29,020
You make me anxious.

206
00:10:29,980 --> 00:10:31,900
I know. I'll be more careful next time.

207
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:32,950
You must remember.

208
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:34,590
She said she was late

209
00:10:34,590 --> 00:10:35,980
because she was reading.

210
00:10:35,980 --> 00:10:37,230
She didn't do it on purpose.

211
00:10:38,710 --> 00:10:39,620
Go back and sleep.

212
00:10:43,830 --> 00:10:44,350
Wait,

213
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:46,660
why doesn't Qingyu need to work?

214
00:10:46,660 --> 00:10:48,260
She's the only one who can have peace.

215
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,590
I want to go to the library too.

216
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,160
Why do you want to go there?

217
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:51,710
Read books.

218
00:10:52,590 --> 00:10:54,260
I'm sure
you're going there to play games.

219
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:00,380
All of you are biased.

220
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:12,500
Yu,

221
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:16,080
I finally know why Mom and Dad

222
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:17,710
won't explain
Qiao Beiyu's cause of death.

223
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:20,110
Why?

224
00:11:20,110 --> 00:11:22,590
Because the rumors are the truth.

225
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:23,550
What?

226
00:11:24,310 --> 00:11:27,190
Are you saying that she died from AIDS?

227
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:30,070
Although I was reluctant
to admit it in the past,

228
00:11:30,070 --> 00:11:31,430
I subconsciously figured

229
00:11:31,430 --> 00:11:33,080
there was something wrong

230
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,430
with Qiao Beiyu's cause of death

231
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,660
because the reaction from Mom and Dad,
her friends, and family members

232
00:11:37,660 --> 00:11:40,710
would only make sense

233
00:11:40,710 --> 00:11:41,950
if she had that disease.

234
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:45,660
However, Mom and Dad kept denying it

235
00:11:46,260 --> 00:11:49,190
so I thought there was
more to her illness than meets the eye.

236
00:11:50,070 --> 00:11:52,350
All the effort I put in
to clear her name

237
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:53,830
was in vain.

238
00:11:53,830 --> 00:11:54,880
What evidence did you find?

239
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,780
She had a medical record
at the People's Hospital.

240
00:11:57,260 --> 00:11:58,600
She did have the disease

241
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,660
that everyone talked about.

242
00:12:00,260 --> 00:12:04,020
Our whole family still has to suffer.

243
00:12:04,710 --> 00:12:05,110
What?

244
00:12:05,110 --> 00:12:07,190
It seems like those rumors are all true.

245
00:12:08,140 --> 00:12:08,860
Moreover,

246
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:11,740
she had a miscarriage
at Nanqiao Village.

247
00:12:12,980 --> 00:12:13,710
Really?

248
00:12:15,310 --> 00:12:16,430
How do you know that?

249
00:12:16,430 --> 00:12:17,740
I met Aunt Xiuzhen today.

250
00:12:17,740 --> 00:12:19,380
She told me about it.

251
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:20,140
Do you think

252
00:12:21,190 --> 00:12:23,950
this is the man who caused her death?

253
00:12:23,950 --> 00:12:25,830
Don't say something without evidence.

254
00:12:27,710 --> 00:12:29,550
(I must find out)

255
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:31,660
(who this person is.)

256
00:12:43,660 --> 00:12:44,310
Mumu.

257
00:12:46,762 --> 00:12:47,860
Help me out.

258
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:51,740
Give this to Mingsheng.

259
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:53,230
Remember.

260
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:53,800
Don't tell him

261
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:55,800
that I was the one
who asked you to give it to him.

262
00:12:58,500 --> 00:12:59,470
Don't worry.

263
00:12:59,470 --> 00:13:00,660
Thank you.

264
00:13:01,230 --> 00:13:01,740
Goodbye.

265
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:15,660
Nice.

266
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:16,740
Check the ball.

267
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:19,350
Look.

268
00:13:20,310 --> 00:13:21,020
Is he handsome?

269
00:13:21,020 --> 00:13:21,860
So handsome.

270
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:23,740
This picture is really handsome.

271
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:25,590
I'm making it my computer wallpaper.

272
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:27,830
Sheng!

273
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:30,020
Play without me.

274
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:32,020
Let's take a break.

275
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:33,190
Let's rest for a while.

276
00:13:39,070 --> 00:13:41,500
Why do they know each other?

277
00:13:43,310 --> 00:13:44,380
It's the smell of jealousy.

278
00:13:44,830 --> 00:13:45,740
What is it?

279
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:48,310
It's sweet and sour. Very delicious.

280
00:13:48,660 --> 00:13:50,600
Mumu is so pretty.

281
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,660
She's also an ace student.

282
00:13:52,380 --> 00:13:53,740
What are they two talking about?

