Remember your attendance.

615
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:56,390
Don't be late.

616
00:34:57,160 --> 00:34:58,470
You are in different streams now.

617
00:34:58,520 --> 00:34:59,910
The headmaster is watching closely.

618
00:34:59,910 --> 00:35:00,620
Do you hear me?

