00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:14,660
Sheng!

624
00:35:14,660 --> 00:35:15,550
Let's exercise.

625
00:35:15,550 --> 00:35:16,660
Oh. Go ahead.

626
00:35:16,660 --> 00:35:18,780
Sure. We'll go and take the court first.

627
00:35:22,180 --> 00:35:23,030
Are you done?

628
00:35:23,340 --> 00:35:24,260
Wait for me.

629
00:35:25,660 --> 00:35:26,740
Let's go.

630
00:35:26,740 --> 00:35:28,300
I don't feel like going home.

631
00:35:28,950 --> 00:35:29,590
Me neither.

632
00:35:30,600 --> 00:35:31,510
Since it's still early,

633
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:33,470
why don't we go play the claw machines?

634
00:35:33,470 --> 00:35:34,070
Let's go.

635
00:35:41,550 --> 00:35:43,550
Help me throw them. You're on duty.

636
00:36:34,470 --> 00:36:36,720
Sheng,
I've been waiting for you for so long.

637
00:36:36,720 --> 00:36:37,660
What are you looking at?

638
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:39,590
Nothing.

639
00:36:40,660 --> 00:36:42,220
Are you stalking Qiao Qingyu?

640
00:36:42,220 --> 00:36:43,510
Why would I stalk her?

641
00:36:43,510 --> 00:36:44,470
Am I crazy or what?

642
00:36:44,470 --> 00:36:45,740
Let's go and play basketball.

643
00:36:45,740 --> 00:36:46,260
No.

644
00:36:46,870 --> 00:36:47,180
Why?

645
00:36:47,700 --> 00:36:49,110
I'm busy so I'll be leaving.

646
00:36:54,820 --> 00:36:56,110
Why do Qiao Qingyu's shoes

647
00:36:56,110 --> 00:36:57,820
look the same as Sheng's?

648
00:36:57,820 --> 00:36:59,300
Are they Sheng's shoes?

649
00:36:59,590 --> 00:37:00,990
Let's go and play some basketball.

650
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:02,870
I know.

651
00:37:02,870 --> 00:37:04,910
I'm going back to the shop.

652
00:37:04,910 --> 00:37:05,480
Sure. Tell him

653
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,840
that I'll return in 20 minutes.

654
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,430
That's all.

655
00:37:11,780 --> 00:37:13,300
Whose shoes are these?

656
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:15,340
Where are your shoes?

657
00:37:16,140 --> 00:37:17,040
I lost my shoes.

658
00:37:17,040 --> 00:37:19,220
I picked up someone else's shoes
from the rubbish bin.

659
00:37:19,220 --> 00:37:19,840
You're an adult.

660
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,070
How did you lose your shoes?

661
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:22,260
Where did you leave them?

662
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:24,990
Moreover, the shoes look fine.

663
00:37:24,990 --> 00:37:26,300
Why would someone throw them away?

664
00:37:28,390 --> 00:37:29,300
Qiao Qingyu.

665
00:37:29,300 --> 00:37:30,840
You'd never find these shoes
in the trash

666
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:32,340
unless someone wants you to wear them.

667
00:37:32,340 --> 00:37:32,960
What's going on?

668
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:34,320
Why don't you wear your own shoes

669
00:37:34,380 --> 00:37:35,510
but a pair of men's shoes?

670
00:37:35,510 --> 00:37:36,740
That was what happened.

671
00:37:36,740 --> 00:37:37,990
I lost my shoes.

672
00:37:37,990 --> 00:37:39,990
Coincidentally, a kind-hearted man

673
00:37:39,990 --> 00:37:42,070
threw away a pair of new shoes
which you picked up?

674
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:44,870
You don't even lie with logic.

675
00:37:46,140 --> 00:37:47,820
A girl putting on a pair of men's shoes.

676
00:37:47,820 --> 00:37:49,390
Where are your principles?

677
00:37:49,390 --> 00:37:50,660
What happened? Tell me!

678
00:37:51,740 --> 00:37:52,660
You're back?

679
00:37:59,030 --> 00:37:59,740
Mom.

680
00:38:00,620 --> 00:38:02,620
Qingyu was bullied

681
00:38:02,620 --> 00:38:04,510
in school.

682
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:06,620
For some reason, Qiao Beiyu's incident

683
00:38:06,620 --> 00:38:08,030
was dug out.

684
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:11,430
The rumor spread like wildfire
on the internet.

685
00:38:11,430 --> 00:38:12,660
Not just Qingyu.

686
00:38:12,660 --> 00:38:15,300
I'm also affected at the Sports School.

687
00:38:25,950 --> 00:38:28,220
Qingyu, I was too anxious just now.

688
00:38:30,510 --> 00:38:32,260
I know you've been aggrieved in school.

689
00:38:33,140 --> 00:38:35,180
Why didn't you tell me anything?

690
00:38:36,660 --> 00:38:37,780
You've been looking gloomy

691
00:38:37,780 --> 00:38:39,440
since coming back from Nanqiao Village.

692
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:40,550
You don't even speak a lot.

693
00:38:41,180 --> 00:38:42,780
I can't read minds

694
00:38:43,820 --> 00:38:45,550
and I'm busy working at the shop.

695
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:48,260
You need to tell me
if something happens to you, right?

696
00:38:53,740 --> 00:38:55,590
Qingyu, we spent so much effort

697
00:38:55,590 --> 00:38:56,910
to come here to study

698
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:59,110
for the sake of
getting into a good university

699
00:38:59,110 --> 00:39:00,510
and having a better future.

700
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:01,820
At a time like this,

701
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:03,950
we need to endure it.

702
00:39:04,660 --> 00:39:06,070
We have to lie low and stay humble.

703
00:39:06,070 --> 00:39:07,620
We can't explain things sometimes.

704
00:39:07,620 --> 00:39:09,390
The more you try to explain,
the worse it gets.

705
00:39:11,070 --> 00:39:12,640
No matter how badly they talk about you,

706
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:15,300
just endure it and it'll be over.

707
00:39:17,110 --> 00:39:18,070
As time goes on,

708
00:39:19,390 --> 00:39:20,640
everything will be forgotten.

709
00:39:21,870 --> 00:39:22,910
I must leave.

710
00:39:24,340 --> 00:39:25,910
Lunch is ready. It's in the pot.

711
00:39:27,990 --> 00:39:29,300
I have to rush back to the shop.

712
00:39:45,300 --> 00:39:47,990
If I hadn't told the truth,

713
00:39:47,990 --> 00:39:49,740
