an earful even now.

714
00:39:51,140 --> 00:39:52,550
What did Mom tell you?

715
00:39:53,780 --> 00:39:54,620
Nothing much.

716
00:39:55,820 --> 00:39:58,070
I heard her say many things to you.

717
00:39:58,740 --> 00:40:00,470
She's always doing this.

718
00:40:00,470 --> 00:40:02,590
She wants me to tell her everything,

719
00:40:02,590 --> 00:40:03,870
but she's also stubborn

720
00:40:03,870 --> 00:40:05,550
and wants me
to follow everything she says.

721
00:40:06,300 --> 00:40:08,780
I think
she doesn't want to listen to me at all.

722
00:40:08,780 --> 00:40:10,030
Maybe adults are all like that.

723
00:40:13,510 --> 00:40:14,740
Actually,

724
00:40:15,700 --> 00:40:18,590
