734
00:40:41,870 --> 00:40:43,550
Even so, we can't just forget about it.

735
00:40:44,910 --> 00:40:46,550
Qiao Beiyu was so pretty.

736
00:40:46,990 --> 00:40:49,470
She did have many boyfriends.

737
00:40:49,470 --> 00:40:51,070
I saw a few of them personally.

738
00:40:51,950 --> 00:40:54,220
However, who was

739
00:40:54,950 --> 00:40:56,110
the Nanqiao Village boyfriend?

