744
00:42:01,190 --> 00:42:06,540
♪Counting the distance between us♪

745
00:42:07,440 --> 00:42:13,700
♪Just one step away from reaching♪

746
00:42:18,700 --> 00:42:20,990
♪The future♪

747
00:42:22,690 --> 00:42:28,310
♪Time will unveil this mystery♪

748
00:42:29,890 --> 00:42:35,250
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

749
00:42:36,100 --> 00:42:42,410
♪But one that never expires♪

750
00:42:44,730 --> 00:42:49,780
♪Turns out, all my thoughts♪

751
00:42:49,880 --> 00:42:54,190
♪Spell your name♪

