00:43:00,710 --> 00:43:04,020
♪From the very first glance♪

754
00:43:04,370 --> 00:43:08,440
♪I started painting
what our future would look like♪

755
00:43:08,440 --> 00:43:14,710
♪That's when the dream began
to feel real♪

756
00:43:14,710 --> 00:43:18,370
♪Turns out♪

757
00:43:18,690 --> 00:43:22,750
♪Your heart had a place for me too♪

758
00:43:23,150 --> 00:43:29,130
♪Cradling the same story we both knew♪

759
00:43:29,400 --> 00:43:33,060
♪Thankfully, we were naïve enough♪

760
00:43:33,060 --> 00:43:36,600
♪And brave just in time♪

